386
00:16:20,740 --> 00:16:21,259
[SPEAKER_00] uprostavim,

387
00:16:21,259 --> 00:16:22,080
[SPEAKER_00] možda malo vićem,

388
00:16:22,080 --> 00:16:22,460
[SPEAKER_00] ali evo,

389
00:16:22,460 --> 00:16:23,580
[SPEAKER_00] to je za vaše dobro.

390
00:16:25,360 --> 00:16:26,419
[SPEAKER_00] kao svećenik,

391
00:16:26,419 --> 00:16:27,740
[SPEAKER_00] kao studenci kapelan,

392
00:16:27,740 --> 00:16:29,519
[SPEAKER_00] često sam okružen

393
00:16:29,519 --> 00:16:30,080
[SPEAKER_00] s ljudima

394
00:16:30,080 --> 00:16:32,080
[SPEAKER_00] koji vjeruju u Boga

395
00:16:32,080 --> 00:16:35,840
[SPEAKER_00] i baš često se onda

396
00:16:35,840 --> 00:16:36,740
[SPEAKER_00] nekad iznenadim.

397
00:16:36,740 --> 00:16:38,320
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, kad vi,

398
00:16:38,320 --> 00:16:39,960
[SPEAKER_00] katolici, kršćani,

399
00:16:39,960 --> 00:16:41,100
[SPEAKER_00] vjernici,

400
00:16:41,100 --> 00:16:42,539
[SPEAKER_00] doćete mi sa nekakvim

401
00:16:42,539 --> 00:16:43,659
[SPEAKER_00] takvim zastranjenjima

402
00:16:43,659 --> 00:16:44,700
[SPEAKER_00] u vjeri.

403
00:16:44,700 --> 00:16:45,940
[SPEAKER_00] S nekakvim u vjerenjima

404
00:16:45,940 --> 00:16:47,320
[SPEAKER_00] koji su krivo vas,

405
00:16:47,320 --> 00:16:47,820
[SPEAKER_00] evo,

406
00:16:47,820 --> 00:16:48,720
[SPEAKER_00] hranila negdje.

407
00:16:49,519 --> 00:16:51,240
[SPEAKER_00] I tada zastranjenja zapravo,

408
00:16:51,240 --> 00:16:53,820
[SPEAKER_00] i to sam proučavao

409
00:16:53,820 --> 00:16:54,960
[SPEAKER_00] malo crkveni dokument

410
00:16:54,960 --> 00:16:55,860
[SPEAKER_00] Gaudete,

411
00:16:55,860 --> 00:16:57,720
[SPEAKER_00] egzultate od pape Franje,

412
00:16:57,720 --> 00:16:59,039
[SPEAKER_00] koji govori

413
00:16:59,039 --> 00:17:00,240
[SPEAKER_00] da zastranjenja

414
00:17:00,240 --> 00:17:01,059
[SPEAKER_00] u vjeri

415
00:17:01,059 --> 00:17:01,820
[SPEAKER_00] koja se događaju

416
00:17:01,820 --> 00:17:02,899
[SPEAKER_00] danas kod kršćana,

417
00:17:02,899 --> 00:17:04,220
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo kod mladih kršćana,

418
00:17:04,220 --> 00:17:06,000
[SPEAKER_00] su ponavljanja

419
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:08,380
[SPEAKER_00] onih starih hereza

420
00:17:08,380 --> 00:17:09,500
[SPEAKER_00] koji su kršćani

421
00:17:09,500 --> 00:17:10,779
[SPEAKER_00] i živjeli u početcima.

422
00:17:10,779 --> 00:17:12,799
[SPEAKER_00] Nevjerovatne stvari,

423
00:17:12,799 --> 00:17:13,279
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi moji.

424
00:17:13,279 --> 00:17:14,720
[SPEAKER_00] Mi danas

425
00:17:14,720 --> 00:17:16,440
[SPEAKER_00] živimo neke poteškoće

426
00:17:16,440 --> 00:17:17,200
[SPEAKER_00] u našoj vjeri,

427
00:17:17,200 --> 00:17:18,759
[SPEAKER_00] neke sumnje,

428
00:17:18,980 --> 00:17:20,980
[SPEAKER_00] neke zastranjenja

429
00:17:20,980 --> 00:17:22,259
[SPEAKER_00] koji su živjeli kršćani

430
00:17:22,259 --> 00:17:24,599
[SPEAKER_00] prije 1800-1700 godina.

431
00:17:24,599 --> 00:17:26,099
[SPEAKER_00] Iste dinamike,

432
00:17:26,099 --> 00:17:27,619
[SPEAKER_00] samo ih drugčije nazivamo,

433
00:17:27,619 --> 00:17:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] drugčije ih oblikujemo,

434
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:30,359
[SPEAKER_00] drugčije ih doživljavamo.

435
00:17:30,359 --> 00:17:32,140
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ajmo vidjeti

436
00:17:32,140 --> 00:17:33,539
[SPEAKER_00] što su uopće to bile hereze,

437
00:17:33,539 --> 00:17:34,799
[SPEAKER_00] da bi onda vidjeli

438
00:17:34,799 --> 00:17:36,160
[SPEAKER_00] koje su to hereze danas

439
00:17:36,160 --> 00:17:36,839
[SPEAKER_00] koje mi živimo,

440
00:17:36,839 --> 00:17:38,420
[SPEAKER_00] koje su to zastranjenja

441
00:17:38,420 --> 00:17:39,119
[SPEAKER_00] u našoj vjeri.

442
00:17:39,119 --> 00:17:40,900
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, prije svega,

443
00:17:40,900 --> 00:17:42,339
[SPEAKER_00] što je to hereza,

444
00:17:42,339 --> 00:17:43,819
[SPEAKER_00] to je krivo vjerje?

445
00:17:43,819 --> 00:17:46,279
[SPEAKER_00] Kategizam katoličke crkve

446
00:17:46,279 --> 00:17:48,440
[SPEAKER_00] na članku

447
00:17:48,440 --> 00:17:49,900
[SPEAKER_00] 2089.

448
00:17:49,900 --> 00:17:51,720
[SPEAKER_00] Krivo vjerje

449
00:17:51,720 --> 00:17:53,720
[SPEAKER_00] je uporno njekanje

450
00:17:53,720 --> 00:17:55,839
[SPEAKER_00] poslije primljenog krsta,

451
00:17:55,839 --> 00:17:56,880
[SPEAKER_00] znači moraš biti kršten.

452
00:17:56,880 --> 00:17:57,799
[SPEAKER_00] Ne možeš biti heretik

453
00:17:57,799 --> 00:17:58,559
[SPEAKER_00] ako nisi kršten.

454
00:18:00,440 --> 00:18:02,799
[SPEAKER_00] uporno njekanje neke istine

455
00:18:02,799 --> 00:18:04,119
[SPEAKER_00] koja treba da se vjeruje

456
00:18:04,119 --> 00:18:05,859
[SPEAKER_00] božanskom i katoličkom vjerom

457
00:18:05,859 --> 00:18:07,980
[SPEAKER_00] ili uporno sumnjanje u nju.

458
00:18:07,980 --> 00:18:11,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ja volim reći da su hereze,

459
00:18:11,380 --> 00:18:12,960
[SPEAKER_00] laži,

460
00:18:12,960 --> 00:18:14,980
[SPEAKER_00] kojima nas je neko hranio,

461
00:18:14,980 --> 00:18:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] koji su, nažalost,

462
00:18:17,160 --> 00:18:18,480
[SPEAKER_00] oblikovale naš um,

463
00:18:18,480 --> 00:18:19,200
[SPEAKER_00] naše srce.

464
00:18:19,200 --> 00:18:20,900
[SPEAKER_00] I te hereze,

465
00:18:20,900 --> 00:18:21,759
[SPEAKER_00] te laži,

466
00:18:21,759 --> 00:18:24,099
[SPEAKER_00] su laži koje dolaze zna pakla.

467
00:18:24,099 --> 00:18:25,839
[SPEAKER_00] Dolaze od samoga sotone,

468
00:18:25,839 --> 00:18:26,960
[SPEAKER_00] od samoga neprijatelja.

469
00:18:26,960 --> 00:18:29,240
[SPEAKER_00] I to s jednim, jedinim razlogom.

470
00:18:29,240 --> 00:18:30,380
[SPEAKER_00] A to je

471
00:18:30,380 --> 00:18:32,220
[SPEAKER_00] da on uništi crkvu,

472
00:18:32,220 --> 00:18:34,480
[SPEAKER_00] njegovo živo tijelo,

473
00:18:34,480 --> 00:18:35,759
[SPEAKER_00] mistično tijelo,

474
00:18:36,440 --> 00:18:37,859
[SPEAKER_00] i da nas udalje od Krista.

475
00:18:37,859 --> 00:18:41,460
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, dragi mladi,

476
00:18:41,460 --> 00:18:43,339
[SPEAKER_00] kad pogledamo malo u povijest,

477
00:18:43,339 --> 00:18:46,140
[SPEAKER_00] crkva kad se rađala u povojima,

478
00:18:46,140 --> 00:18:48,240
[SPEAKER_00] s njom su se uvijek rađale

479
00:18:48,240 --> 00:18:49,460
[SPEAKER_00] i neke nove hereze.

480
00:18:49,460 --> 00:18:51,920
[SPEAKER_00] Šta su bile te hereze?

481
00:18:51,920 --> 00:18:53,700
[SPEAKER_00] To je bio napad na istine

482
00:18:53,700 --> 00:18:55,440
[SPEAKER_00] koje je katolička crkva smatrala

483
00:18:55,440 --> 00:18:56,380
[SPEAKER_00] temeljnima.

484
00:18:56,380 --> 00:18:58,859
[SPEAKER_00] Mi kad danas čujemo riječ hereza,

485
00:18:58,859 --> 00:19:00,099
[SPEAKER_00] ja vjerujem da vam ona zvuči

486
00:19:00,099 --> 00:19:01,079
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo arhajično.

487
00:19:01,079 --> 00:19:02,420
[SPEAKER_00] Nešto što pripada povijesti,

488
00:19:02,420 --> 00:19:03,880
[SPEAKER_00] daleko i tako dalje i tako dalje.

489
00:19:03,880 --> 00:19:05,480
[SPEAKER_00] Nešto zastarjelo,

490
00:19:05,859 --> 00:19:07,240
[SPEAKER_00] što više nije aktualno.

491
00:19:07,240 --> 00:19:09,519
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, nevjerovatna stvar,

492
00:19:09,519 --> 00:19:10,480
[SPEAKER_00] i to ćemo vidjeti kasnije,

493
00:19:10,480 --> 00:19:12,440
[SPEAKER_00] da neke hereze se danas ponavljaju.

494
00:19:12,440 --> 00:19:13,200
[SPEAKER_00] Mi živimo,

495
00:19:13,200 --> 00:19:14,599
[SPEAKER_00] a da toga nismo ni svjesni.

496
00:19:14,599 --> 00:19:17,720
[SPEAKER_00] U početku crkva je bila jako mlada.

497
00:19:17,720 --> 00:19:19,359
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, možemo reći,

498
00:19:19,359 --> 00:19:20,900
[SPEAKER_00] poput jedne male biljčice,

499
00:19:20,900 --> 00:19:21,759
[SPEAKER_00] mlade biljke.

500
00:19:21,759 --> 00:19:24,819
[SPEAKER_00] Isus oko sebe okuplja 12 apostola.

501
00:19:24,819 --> 00:19:26,500
[SPEAKER_00] Utemeljuje crkvu,

502
00:19:26,500 --> 00:19:28,019
[SPEAKER_00] dao im je duha svetoga da idu,

503
00:19:28,019 --> 00:19:30,380
[SPEAKER_00] propovijedaju po svem svijetu

504
00:19:30,380 --> 00:19:31,539
[SPEAKER_00] radosnu vijest evanđelja.

505
00:19:31,539 --> 00:19:33,259
[SPEAKER_00] Vrlo brzo,

506
00:19:33,259 --> 00:19:34,539
[SPEAKER_00] ono što možemo primijetiti,

507
00:19:34,680 --> 00:19:35,599
[SPEAKER_00] već u svetome pismo,

508
00:19:35,599 --> 00:19:37,079
[SPEAKER_00] a to je da je crkva prepoznala

509
00:19:37,079 --> 00:19:38,720
[SPEAKER_00] potrebu za strukturom.

510
00:19:38,720 --> 00:19:40,660
[SPEAKER_00] Važnost strukture,

511
00:19:40,660 --> 00:19:42,180
[SPEAKER_00] važnost hierarhije,

512
00:19:42,180 --> 00:19:45,759
[SPEAKER_00] važnost učiteljstva.

513
00:19:45,759 --> 00:19:49,059
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, da postoji nekakva važnost strukture,

514
00:19:49,059 --> 00:19:50,579
[SPEAKER_00] da ne može bilo ko šta blenuti

515
00:19:50,579 --> 00:19:51,759
[SPEAKER_00] i sad mi to svi vjerujemo.

516
00:19:51,759 --> 00:19:53,799
[SPEAKER_00] Da nije svejedno

517
00:19:53,799 --> 00:19:55,099
[SPEAKER_00] od kog slušaš te stvari,

518
00:19:55,099 --> 00:19:56,319
[SPEAKER_00] s kim se hraniš,

519
00:19:56,319 --> 00:19:57,480
[SPEAKER_00] od koga čitaš stvari

520
00:19:57,480 --> 00:19:58,680
[SPEAKER_00] s kojima se hrani,

521
00:19:58,680 --> 00:19:59,660
[SPEAKER_00] hraniš svoj duhonos,

522
00:19:59,660 --> 00:20:00,180
[SPEAKER_00] svoj život.

523
00:20:00,180 --> 00:20:03,720
[SPEAKER_00] Evo i baš zbog toga

524
00:20:03,720 --> 00:20:05,299
[SPEAKER_00] što su apostoli bili često

525
00:20:05,299 --> 00:20:07,460
[SPEAKER_00] ne baš velikog znanja

526
00:20:07,460 --> 00:20:09,079
[SPEAKER_00] u tom trenutku,

527
00:20:09,079 --> 00:20:11,279
[SPEAKER_00] a izazovi pri njima su bili

528
00:20:11,279 --> 00:20:13,380
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo žestoki,

529
00:20:13,380 --> 00:20:16,160
[SPEAKER_00] trebali su drugima govoriti

530
00:20:16,160 --> 00:20:17,519
[SPEAKER_00] ono što im je Isus ostavio,

531
00:20:17,619 --> 00:20:19,299
[SPEAKER_00] to je skomunicirati radosnu vijest,

532
00:20:19,299 --> 00:20:20,839
[SPEAKER_00] upravo zbog toga

533
00:20:20,839 --> 00:20:22,079
[SPEAKER_00] ostatili su potrebu

534
00:20:22,079 --> 00:20:24,180
[SPEAKER_00] evo, da napravi strukturu,

535
00:20:24,180 --> 00:20:25,220
[SPEAKER_00] da se oforme.

536
00:20:25,220 --> 00:20:29,279
[SPEAKER_00] I u početku crkva se susreće,

537
00:20:29,279 --> 00:20:30,140
[SPEAKER_00] što je normalno,

538
00:20:30,140 --> 00:20:32,839
[SPEAKER_00] sa pluralnošću mišljenja.

539
00:20:32,839 --> 00:20:34,440
[SPEAKER_00] Jako puno ljudi,

540
00:20:34,440 --> 00:20:35,799
[SPEAKER_00] jako puno drugčih naroda,

541
00:20:35,799 --> 00:20:37,019
[SPEAKER_00] jako puno razmišljenja,

542
00:20:37,019 --> 00:20:38,859
[SPEAKER_00] jako puno pogalnuka oko njih.

543
00:20:38,859 --> 00:20:39,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ok?

544
00:20:39,119 --> 00:20:40,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ne samo izvana.

545
00:20:40,880 --> 00:20:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta se događalo?

546
00:20:42,000 --> 00:20:42,619
[SPEAKER_00] Često

547
00:20:42,619 --> 00:20:44,539
[SPEAKER_00] taj pogalnuk,

548
00:20:44,539 --> 00:20:46,339
[SPEAKER_00] to je ta zastranjenja,

549
00:20:47,079 --> 00:20:48,779
[SPEAKER_00] događala su se iznutra.

550
00:20:48,779 --> 00:20:50,259
[SPEAKER_00] Te hereze,

551
00:20:50,259 --> 00:20:51,420
[SPEAKER_00] najčešće u crkvi,

552
00:20:51,420 --> 00:20:52,460
[SPEAKER_00] rađali su se iznutra.

553
00:20:52,460 --> 00:20:53,420
[SPEAKER_00] Čuli smo danas,

554
00:20:53,420 --> 00:20:54,799
[SPEAKER_00] ne možeš biti heretik

555
00:20:54,799 --> 00:20:56,019
[SPEAKER_00] ako nisi kršten.

556
00:20:56,019 --> 00:20:58,579
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, i budući da je kršćanstvo

557
00:20:58,579 --> 00:21:00,460
[SPEAKER_00] postojalo sve masovnije i masovnije,

558
00:21:00,460 --> 00:21:02,980
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi su imali različite doživljave,

559
00:21:02,980 --> 00:21:04,339
[SPEAKER_00] različito iskustvo.

560
00:21:04,339 --> 00:21:06,380
[SPEAKER_00] I počele su događati

561
00:21:06,380 --> 00:21:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] da su se na različit način,

562
00:21:08,000 --> 00:21:08,700
[SPEAKER_00] nažalost,

563
00:21:08,700 --> 00:21:10,160
[SPEAKER_00] tumačile Isusove riječi,

564
00:21:10,160 --> 00:21:10,859
[SPEAKER_00] Isov nauk.

565
00:21:10,859 --> 00:21:13,200
[SPEAKER_00] I te opasnosti, ponavljam,

566
00:21:13,200 --> 00:21:15,400
[SPEAKER_00] nisu dolazile izvana crkve,

567
00:21:15,680 --> 00:21:16,859
[SPEAKER_00] nego unutar crkve.

568
00:21:16,859 --> 00:21:19,440
[SPEAKER_00] I to vidimo već u prvim poslanicima.

569
00:21:19,440 --> 00:21:21,559
[SPEAKER_00] Sveti Pavao govori

570
00:21:21,559 --> 00:21:24,059
[SPEAKER_00] vrlo oštro i britko

571
00:21:24,059 --> 00:21:26,359
[SPEAKER_00] o takozvanim lažnim učiteljima,

572
00:21:26,359 --> 00:21:27,400
[SPEAKER_00] lažnim prorocima.

573
00:21:27,400 --> 00:21:30,779
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko danas lažni proroka oko nas?

574
00:21:30,779 --> 00:21:32,819
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko ljudi koji tvrde za sebe

575
00:21:32,819 --> 00:21:34,019
[SPEAKER_00] da imaju rješenje za naš život?

576
00:21:34,019 --> 00:21:36,299
[SPEAKER_00] Da oni znaju

577
00:21:36,299 --> 00:21:38,039
[SPEAKER_00] kako ćemo neke stvari

578
00:21:38,039 --> 00:21:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] poboljšati,

579
00:21:39,000 --> 00:21:40,539
[SPEAKER_00] pouspješiti.

580
00:21:41,180 --> 00:21:42,940
[SPEAKER_00] Na kraju krajeva kako ćemo biti sretni?

581
00:21:45,500 --> 00:21:47,259
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže Pavao u jednom trenutku

582
00:21:47,259 --> 00:21:48,480
[SPEAKER_00] u Galačanima 1.9

583
00:21:48,480 --> 00:21:49,839
[SPEAKER_00] Čak i kad bi vam

584
00:21:49,839 --> 00:21:51,539
[SPEAKER_00] anđeo s neba navješivao

585
00:21:51,539 --> 00:21:52,460
[SPEAKER_00] u neko evanđelje,

586
00:21:52,460 --> 00:21:53,859
[SPEAKER_00] mimo onoga

587
00:21:53,859 --> 00:21:55,359
[SPEAKER_00] koje vam mi navijestismo,

588
00:21:55,359 --> 00:21:56,579
[SPEAKER_00] neka je proklet.

589
00:21:56,579 --> 00:21:59,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi moj, ovo su žestoke stvari.

590
00:21:59,039 --> 00:22:00,339
[SPEAKER_00] To sve ti Pavao govori.

591
00:22:01,259 --> 00:22:02,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ako postoji jedno evanđelje,

592
00:22:02,440 --> 00:22:03,180
[SPEAKER_00] ako vam neko govori

593
00:22:03,180 --> 00:22:04,480
[SPEAKER_00] jedno evanđelje sa strane

594
00:22:04,480 --> 00:22:05,519
[SPEAKER_00] koje nije ono

595
00:22:05,519 --> 00:22:06,559
[SPEAKER_00] koje smo mi navijestili,

596
00:22:06,559 --> 00:22:07,500
[SPEAKER_00] neka je proklet.

597
00:22:07,500 --> 00:22:11,119
[SPEAKER_00] Crkva je jako brzo shvatila

598
00:22:11,119 --> 00:22:13,740
[SPEAKER_00] da treba produbljivati svoj nauk.

599
00:22:13,740 --> 00:22:16,799
[SPEAKER_00] Da ono što su znali na početku

600
00:22:16,799 --> 00:22:17,500
[SPEAKER_00] nije dovoljno.

601
00:22:17,500 --> 00:22:20,160
[SPEAKER_00] Da treba ju produbljavati istine

602
00:22:20,160 --> 00:22:21,980
[SPEAKER_00] i izgovarati ih na novi način

603
00:22:21,980 --> 00:22:23,559
[SPEAKER_00] za različita vremena,

604
00:22:23,559 --> 00:22:24,819
[SPEAKER_00] za različite kulture.

605
00:22:24,819 --> 00:22:26,619
[SPEAKER_00] I tako se malo pomalo

606
00:22:26,619 --> 00:22:28,559
