607
00:22:29,019 --> 00:22:31,640
[SPEAKER_00] a s druge strane razvijao se nauk crkve.

608
00:22:31,640 --> 00:22:36,079
[SPEAKER_00] Jako je zanimljivo gledati svata gibanja.

609
00:22:36,079 --> 00:22:37,680
[SPEAKER_00] Nećemo sad daviti s povješću.

610
00:22:37,680 --> 00:22:39,839
[SPEAKER_00] Ja nisam volio povijest u ono vrijeme,

611
00:22:39,839 --> 00:22:40,819
