615
00:22:47,539 --> 00:22:47,980
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

616
00:22:47,980 --> 00:22:51,200
[SPEAKER_00] Zato jer su natjerale crkvene pastire

617
00:22:51,200 --> 00:22:53,119
