619
00:22:55,920 --> 00:22:58,039
[SPEAKER_00] Drugim riječima, svaka hereza

620
00:22:58,039 --> 00:22:59,740
[SPEAKER_00] na neki način je ubrzala crkvu

621
00:22:59,740 --> 00:23:03,119
[SPEAKER_00] da da odgovor na provokaciju,

622
00:23:03,119 --> 00:23:04,660
[SPEAKER_00] na napadnutu istinu.

623
00:23:04,660 --> 00:23:06,599
[SPEAKER_00] I crkva se morala brzo snalaziti.

624
00:23:06,599 --> 00:23:07,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi mojim pučetcima,

625
00:23:07,880 --> 00:23:09,440
[SPEAKER_00] sabori su bili svako toliko.

626
00:23:09,440 --> 00:23:11,619
[SPEAKER_00] Papa bi okupio sve biskupe

627
00:23:11,619 --> 00:23:12,519
