630
00:23:15,140 --> 00:23:16,339
[SPEAKER_00] važnim istinama crkve.

631
00:23:17,599 --> 00:23:19,140
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna prekrasna scena

632
00:23:19,140 --> 00:23:20,500
