641
00:23:30,019 --> 00:23:31,119
[SPEAKER_00] koji nosi darove djeci.

642
00:23:31,119 --> 00:23:32,900
[SPEAKER_00] Imate prekrasnu sliku

643
00:23:32,900 --> 00:23:33,720
[SPEAKER_00] svetoga Nikole

644
