650
00:23:41,779 --> 00:23:42,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, preblizu sam.

651
00:23:42,880 --> 00:23:45,859
[SPEAKER_00] Ovoga, ne, ovoga, da.

652
00:23:45,859 --> 00:23:47,940
[SPEAKER_00] Još s ovim mahanjem.

653
00:23:47,940 --> 00:23:49,859
